snippet.title: CLASS | Zakir khan | Stand up Comedy | Sukha Puri 8
snippet.description:
Watch Zakir Khan Live In your city Tickets: https://zakirkhanlive.in 

INSTAGRAM : - https://www.instagram.com/zakirkhan_208?igsh=MTBtNzVvNW1xOTYyag==
.
.

Get ready to laugh out loud with Zakir Khan in this stand-up comedy video where he dives into the rollercoaster ride of relationships! Zakir takes on the role of a funny relationship coach, sharing his hilarious tips and relatable stories about love's ups and downs. With his unique style of mixing humor with real-life advice, he makes understanding relationships a fun experience. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy as Zakir Khan shows us how to navigate the crazy world of love while keeping it lighthearted and entertaining!

Director: Karan Asnani
DOP: Gaurav Anand
Video Production by Myoho Films & Vision of GAP

snippet.title: CHICKEN 65 IDLI | Fried Chicken Idli Recipe Cooking In Village | Idli Cooking with Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
n this video, we bring you a unique and mouthwatering recipe, Chicken 65 Idli!  A fusion of South Indian tradition and spicy flavors, this dish combines soft, fluffy idlis with crispy, flavorful fried chicken. Watch as we prepare this innovative recipe in our beautiful village setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional cooking methods.

Whatâ€™s special about this recipe?

The perfect blend of soft idlis and spicy Chicken 65.
Simple steps that you can follow to recreate this dish at home.
A wholesome and flavorful meal for all occasions!
Join us for this delicious adventure filled with authentic village vibes.

In this Josh Talks video, meet Rahul Sinha from Bihar, the founder of the social media channel "Thethar Puns." Rahul has proven that difficult circumstances and financial struggles cannot stop anyone from achieving their dreams. With his hard work and unique approach, he made a name for himself on social media and won the hearts of millions.
Rahul's journey has been full of struggles. Born into a lower-middle-class family, Rahul took on the responsibility of his household by teaching tuition from the 10th grade. Due to financial constraints, he had to drop out of school. These challenging circumstances inspired Rahul to think differently. He started with network marketing but later moved to Mumbai to begin a new chapter in his career.
In the beginning, Rahul created content on several social media platforms, but he did not achieve much success. However, he didnâ€™t give up and launched his YouTube channel "Thethar Puns" on May 28, 2020. He edited videos with speaking faces on inanimate objects like potatoes, onions, buckets, and motorcycles. This unique concept was loved by viewers, and soon his channel gained millions of views and subscribers.
Rahul's channel "Thethar Puns" has now earned a significant reputation. His YouTube channel has 8.85 million subscribers, and his Instagram has 3 million followers. His funny stories have earned him the YouTube Golden Play Button and opportunities like commentary in Bhojpuri for IPL 2024.

Sarathkumar, Prabhu and Khushbu. The film has music composed by Yuvan Shankar Raja, cinematography handled by Om Prakash and Cameron Eric Bryson and editing by A. Sreekar Prasad. Nesippaya is scheduled to release in theatres on 14 January 2025. Nesippaya movie audio launch & trailer happened in Chennai today. Nesippaya Trailer is out now. Sivakarthikeyan invited as chief guest for Nesippaya movie audio & trailer launch. Presenting Sivakarthikeyan speech about Nesippaya.

----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Taarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: 3rd T20I | Highlights | Sri Lanka Tour Of New Zealand | 2nd January 2025
snippet.description:
In the 3rd T20I, Sri Lanka and New Zealand went head-to-head at the Saxton Oval. New Zealand won the toss and asked Sri Lanka to bat first. Sri Lanka posted 218 runs on the board for 5 wickets in their 20 overs. A brilliant 101 runs knock from Kusal Parera helped the Lankans to achieve a huge score. The Kiwis got a decent start and faught tooth and nail to achieve the target but fell short by 7 runs. Rachin Ravindra was the star player from the Kiwis team scoring 69 valuable runs.
.

snippet.title: VENKY MAMAs tho #SankranthikiVasthunam Full Video | Venkatesh | Anil Ravipudi | Dilraju
snippet.description:
Watch team #SankranthikiVasthunam surprises Victory #Venkatesh in his iconic getups for a fun filled interaction!!
____________________

Watch the lyrical videos here!

#GodariGattu : https://youtu.be/L8s6qxQJKgk 

#Meenu Song: https://youtu.be/2_Z5L0Qa0k4 

#BlockbusterPongal: https://youtu.be/S8NDIJBbd3Q  
____________________

Sankranthiki Vasthunam is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #venkateshdaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. Touted as an extraordinary triangular crime entertainer, revolving around three characters- the protagonist, his ex-girlfriend, and his excellent wife. Produced by Sri Venkateswara Creations on a massive scale.

Meenakshi Chaudhary and Aishwarya Rajesh are the heroines opposite Venkatesh. Music is composed by Bheems Ceciroleo, Cinematography by Sameer Reddy, Production Designing by A S Prakash. 

Grand Release WorldWide On Jan 14, 2025. 

Cast:Venkatesh Daggubati, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Aishwarya Rajesh, Upendra Limaye, Sai Kumar, Naresh, VT Ganesh, Prithviraj, Srinivas Avasarala, Muralidhar Goud, Pammi Sai, Sai Srinivas, Anand Raj, Mahesh Balaraj, Pradeep Kabra, and Chitti etc.,
